'''Konknni sevadhormik songit''' mhonghe [[Konknni bhas|Konknni bhasen]] [[Katolik firgoz]]anim uzar kel'lem dhormik songit. [[Gõy and Damanv Mha-Dhormprant]]-a bhair, [[Maharaxhttr]]ache Sindhudurgan and [[Kornattok]]ache Mungllur, Karwar, and Udupint-ui servadhorman Konknni vaportat.

Vatican II uprant Konknnint sevadhorm suru zalem, tednam, Pri. [[Vasco do Rego]], hannem Konknni gaionam borounk fuddem pavl marlem, ani tannem [[Gaionancho Jhelo]] suru kelo.<ref>http://www.goanvoice.ca/2016/issue11/peopleplacesthings.htm#ppt_2</ref><ref>http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/goa/Salvaging-tradition-one-hymn-at-a-time/articleshow/52402467.cms</ref><ref>http://www.heraldgoa.in/Review/The-Sound-Of-Konkani-Gospel-Music/82173.html</ref><ref>https://archive.org/details/FrVascoRego</ref> Pri. [[Lourdino Barreto]] Goencho anik ek xrestt songitkar zaka akhea sounsarak pachartalet.<ref>http://www.dommartin.us/Philantrophy/Fr.%20Lourdino%20Barreto.html</ref>

